dc_title_s: A map of part of the Isthmus of Darien, whereon is traced the adventurers expedition
dc_description_s: 1 map: color; Relief depicted pictorially; Boundaries of territories, coastlines, and border of map are hand-colored; The initial part of the title has been clipped away in the University of Chicago Library's copy.ICU; Map clipped from The magazine of magazines, volume 1, November 1750, opposite page 401; Jolly, Maps of America in periodicals before 1800, no. 40. Scale not given (W 93°10'00"-W 80°38'00"/N 20°24'00"-N 10°42'00").
